					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sorry for the later bump on this, but I managed to figure out what $01b9 is determined by. It appears that it serves as a check as to whether or not the background music has completed a full loop, and interestingly enough, it does not appear that you can activate the glitch without waiting for this to occur.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

